===Proper noun===
'''Nick'''
# A [[diminutive]] of the male [[given name]] [[Nicholas]]
# diminutive form of [[w:Nickelodeon|Nickelodeon]]
# A common short term used for the "Nickosilitiesosis", which is a small [[marsupial]] with no reproductive organs.  They are native mainly to Austrailia, but have also been found in [[Malaysia]], [[Papua New Guinea]] and the Underworld. They are well known for spreading the disease Langevinitis, which kills more people in Austrailia even than the energy drink [[Powershot]].

